OL,3,CAmy Schumer reveals rare health
OL,4,Ccondition after online trolling
OL,6,FComedian and actor Amy Schumer has
OL,7,Frevealed she has Cushing's syndrome
OL,8,Fafter she was on the receiving end of
OL,9,Fonline speculation over her appearance.
OL,11,FSchumer was subjected to social media
OL,12,Fattacks over what people said was her
OL,13,Fchanged appearance when she was guest
OL,14,Fearlier this month on The Tonight Show
OL,15,Fwith Jimmy Fallon.
OL,17,FIn an social media post shortly after
OL,18,Fher appearance on the show, Schumer
OL,19,Fand was experiencing some "medical and
OL,20,Fhormonal things" but confirmed she was
OL,21,F"okay".
