OL,3,CAmy Schumer reveals rare health
OL,4,Ccondition after online trolling
OL,6,FOn Friday, she shared a further update
OL,7,Fwith , revealing she has exogenous
OL,8,FCushing's syndrome, brought on by
OL,9,Fgetting steroid injections in high
OL,10,Fdoses.
OL,12,FCushing's syndrome is a condition
OL,13,Fcaused by having too much of a hormone
OL,14,Fcalled cortisol in your body. It can
OL,15,Fbe serious if it's not treated,
OL,16,Faccording to the NHS.
OL,18,FSchumer said she felt "reborn" after
OL,19,Fher diagnosis.
