OL,6,FShe continued: "So finding out I have
OL,7,Fthe kind of Cushing that will just
OL,8,Fwork itself out and I'm healthy was
OL,9,Fthe greatest news imaginable. It has
OL,10,Fbeen a crazy couple weeks for me and
OL,11,Fmy family. Aside from fears about my
OL,12,Fhealth, I also had to be on camera
OL,13,Fhaving the internet chime in.
OL,15,F"But thank God for that. Because
OL,16,Fthat's how I realised something was
OL,17,Fwrong. Just like when I realised I had
OL,18,Fnamed my son something that didn't
OL,19,Fsound so good. The internet is
OL,20,Fundefeated, as they say.
