OL,6,FSchumer said she wanted to share her
OL,7,Fdiagnosis to advocate for women's
OL,8,Fhealth and body positivity.
OL,10,F"The shaming and criticism of our ever-
OL,11,Fchanging bodies is something I have
OL,12,Fdealt with and witnessed for a long
OL,13,Ftime," Schumer explained.
OL,15,F"I want so much for women to love
OL,16,Fthemselves and be relentless when
OL,17,Ffighting for their own health in a
OL,18,Fsystem that usually doesn't believe
OL,19,Fthem."
